<p>有两棵 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">n</span></span></span></span> 个节点的树，节点编号都为 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">1</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span></span></span></span> 到 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">n</span></span></span></span>。</p>
<p>现在你要构造一个整数数组 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>a</mi><mo>[</mo><mo>]</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">a[]</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">a</span><span class="mopen">[</span><span class="mclose">]</span></span></span></span>，两棵树中编号为 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>i</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">i</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.65952em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">i</span></span></span></span> 的点的权值都为 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>a</mi><mo>[</mo><mi>i</mi><mo>]</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">a[i]</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">a</span><span class="mopen">[</span><span class="mord mathdefault">i</span><span class="mclose">]</span></span></span></span>。</p>
<p>你构造的数组要使得两棵树中每个节点的子树的权值和都为 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">1</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span></span></span></span> 或 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">-1</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.72777em;vertical-align:-0.08333em;"></span><span class="mord">−</span><span class="mord">1</span></span></span></span>。</p>
<p>如果不可能构造这样的数组，输出 <code>Impossible</code>。</p>
<p><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>≤</mo><mn>1</mn><msup><mn>0</mn><mn>5</mn></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">n\le 10^5</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.7719400000000001em;vertical-align:-0.13597em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">n</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">≤</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8141079999999999em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord">0</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.8141079999999999em;"><span style="top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight">5</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<hr>
<p>提示：存在一种方案，<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">∀</mi><mi>i</mi><mo>∈</mo><mo>[</mo><mn>1</mn><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi>n</mi><mo>]</mo><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi>a</mi><mo>[</mo><mi>i</mi><mo>]</mo><mo>∈</mo><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo separator="true">,</mo><mn>0</mn><mo separator="true">,</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\forall i\in [1,n], a[i]\in{-1,0,1}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.73354em;vertical-align:-0.0391em;"></span><span class="mord">∀</span><span class="mord mathdefault">i</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">∈</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mopen">[</span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">n</span><span class="mclose">]</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">a</span><span class="mopen">[</span><span class="mord mathdefault">i</span><span class="mclose">]</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">∈</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8388800000000001em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord">−</span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;"></span><span class="mord">0</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span></span></span></span></span>。</p>
<hr>
<h2 id="欧拉回路-给树上的每条边定向-定向后在树-1-中子节点指向亲节点代表子节点子树权值和为-1-亲节点指向子节点代表子节点子树权值和为-1-这样树-1-中一个点最终的入度减出度就是它的权值而树-2-中最终的出度减入度就是它的权值-这两者要相等">欧拉回路。给树上的每条边定向。定向后，在树 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">1</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span></span></span></span> 中，子节点指向亲节点代表子节点子树权值和为 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">-1</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.72777em;vertical-align:-0.08333em;"></span><span class="mord">−</span><span class="mord">1</span></span></span></span> ，亲节点指向子节点代表子节点子树权值和为 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">1</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span></span></span></span>。这样，树 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">1</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span></span></span></span> 中一个点最终的入度减出度就是它的权值，而树 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">2</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">2</span></span></span></span> 中最终的出度减入度就是它的权值。这两者要相等。</h2>
<ul>
<li>混合图欧拉回路</li>
<li>强联通分量<br>
利用Tarjan，找出low[i]<br>
low[i]=i的情况下i为一个强联通分量的根<br>
推荐题：<a href="https://www.luogu.com.cn/problem/P2341">最受欢迎的牛</a></li>
</ul>
<h1 id="代码">代码</h1>
<pre><code>#include&lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt;
using namespace std;
int timeh;
int n,m,cuo[10010],low[10010],ans,num[10010],gui[10010];
vector&lt;int&gt; to[10010];
stack&lt;int&gt; s;
bool visit[10010],in[10010],v2[10010],out[10010];
void tarjan(int now) { 
//    cout&lt;&lt;&quot;now:&quot;&lt;&lt;now&lt;&lt;endl;
visit[now]=true,s.push(now),timeh++,cuo[now]=timeh,low[now]=timeh,in[now]=true;
for(int i=0; i&lt;to[now].size(); i++) {
	int ti=to[now][i];
	if(!visit[ti]) {
		tarjan(ti);
		low[now]=min(low[now],low[ti]);
	} else if(in[ti]) low[now]=min(low[now],low[ti]);
}
if(low[now]!=cuo[now]) return ;
//	cout&lt;&lt;&quot;我是根&quot;&lt;&lt;now&lt;&lt;endl;
int k;
do{
	k=s.top(),s.pop();
	in[k]=false;
	gui[k]=now;
}while(k!=now);
}
void dfs(int now) {
if(v2[now]) return ;
v2[now]=true;
for(int i=0; i&lt;to[now].size(); i++) {
	int ti=to[now][i];
	if(gui[ti]!=gui[now]) out[gui[now]]=true;
	else dfs(ti);
}
}

int main() {
cin&gt;&gt;n&gt;&gt;m;
for(int i=1; i&lt;=m; i++) {
	int a,b;
	cin&gt;&gt;a&gt;&gt;b;
	to[a].push_back(b);
}	
for(int i=1; i&lt;=n; i++) if(!visit[i]) tarjan(i);
for(int i=1; i&lt;=n; i++) if(!v2[i]) dfs(i);
for(int i=1; i&lt;=n; i++) num[gui[i]]++;
//    for(int i=1; i&lt;=n; i++) cout&lt;&lt;&quot;gui:&quot;&lt;&lt;i&lt;&lt;&quot;:&quot;&lt;&lt;gui[i]&lt;&lt;endl;
for(int i=1; i&lt;=n; i++) if(low[i]==cuo[i]) {
	if(!out[i]) {
		if(ans) {cout&lt;&lt;0&lt;&lt;endl;return 0;}
		else ans=num[i];
	}
}
cout&lt;&lt;ans&lt;&lt;endl;
return 0;
}
</code></pre>
<ul>
<li>
<p>双联通分量<br>
<a href="https://baike.so.com/doc/9441199-9782210.html">百度百科</a><br>
[博客索引](https://www.cnblogs.com/ljk123-de-bo-ke/p/10888905.html）</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>边双联通分量</p>
<ul>
<li>DFS（Tarjan）<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/fuyukai/article/details/51303292">博客索引</a></li>
<li>边双联通图一定有耳朵<br>
<a href="https://zerol.me/2019/03/06/ear-decomposition/">耳分解 博客索引</a></li>
<li>割边肯定是树边</li>
<li>边双联通分量的树上差分算法<br>
对于每一条返祖边，他“覆盖”一些树边。我们把这些树边的“被覆盖次数”+1，最<br>
常数较大，O（n+m），要DFS两遍</li>
<li>边双联通分量例题：Educational Codeforces Round 63 (Rated for Div. 2) F</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>
<p>点双联通分量</p>
<ul>
<li>还是DFS</li>
<li>点u是割点当且仅当u在dfs树上存在一个孩子满足low[v]&gt;=dfn[u]</li>
<li>low[idx[12]]=12&gt;dfn[idx[8]],8是割点</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>
<p>圆方树(block cut tree)</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>kosaraju算法 <a href="https://baike.so.com/doc/8986970-9315633.html">百度百科</a></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>SAT问题<br>
对于一个只含有与，或，非括号和若干遍量的表达式，求一组是的这个表达式为真的解<br>
可以发现，这类表达式最终都能写成一些变量或者变量的非值<br>
如果与号之间的括号里面有k个变量被或起来，我们称之为k-SAT问题</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>2-SAT 即括号里面有两个东西被或起来</p>
<ul>
<li>A蕴含 B 当且仅当 A命题为真，B命题为假时为假</li>
<li>A或B等价于B的非值蕴含A</li>
<li>如果A蕴含B，我们连边A-&gt;B</li>
<li>如果B的非值蕴含A，我们连边：B的非值-&gt;A</li>
<li>忘记了可以现场编</li>
<li>对于一组或的关系，把两条蕴含边连上</li>
<li>每个强联通分量是打包的，必须一起选</li>
<li>如果A和A的非值，就直接凉掉？好像也只能用这个词了</li>
<li>吧缩点后的图反过来</li>
<li>优先选择拓扑序娇小的可选包，选择这个包，然后把和它矛盾的所有包标记为不可选择。</li>
<li>为什么是对的
<ol>
<li>A和非A不会同时被选</li>
<li>要求关系能被满足</li>
<li>A和非A不会都不被选(对称性）</li>
</ol>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>
<p>最短路</p>
<ul>
<li>SPFA(经常被卡)</li>
<li>Belllman-Ford</li>
<li>Dijkstra<br>
用堆优化后还好<br>
用zkw线段树优化（优化算法的难度大于原本算法）</li>
<li>负环<br>
Naive 在SPFA中，如果一个点入队超过N次，那么一定会有负环</li>
<li>差分约束<br>
给定很多形如x_i-x_j&lt;=的式子，不同式子的W可能不一样<br>
求x_s-x_t的最小值</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
]]></content>
    </entry>
